(1400, ' Pierce chuck roast; cover with meat tenderizer and pepper well. Mix marinade of vegetable oil , ketchup , vinegar with garlic and a few shakes of Worcestershire sauce. Cover roast and marinate at least 12 hours. Grill and baste with marinade. Roast has better texture when room temperature before grilling.', ' chuck roast', ' meat tenderizer', ' Worcestershire sauce', '1/2 c. ketchup or A.1.', '1/2 c. vegetable oil', '1/2 c. wine vinegar with garlic', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
