(1530, ' Bake cake as directed in 2 (9-inch) cake pans. When done let cool on plate. Take fork , poking holes in first layer. Add 1 1/4 boxes of strawberries. Carefully spoon on enough Cool Whip to cover cake. Add second layer on top; repeat strawberries and Cool Whip to completely cover cake. Take remaining 1/2 box strawberries and dribble over sides and top of cake. Refrigerate until ready to serve.', '1 box butter flavored cake mix (yellow)', '2 (12 oz.) bowls Cool Whip', '3 pt. boxes sweetened strawberries', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
