(4272, ' Cook beef and onion; drain. Stir in tomatoes and next 7 ingredients. Bring to boil. Reduce heat; simmer , stirring occasionally , about 30 minutes. Add next 3 ingredients and simmer 15 minutes. Stir in pasta. Pour into soup bowls and sprinkle with Parmesan cheese for each serving.', '1 lb. ground beef', '1 onion , chopped', '2 cans Italian tomatoes', '1 can tomato soup', '4 c. water', '1 clove garlic', '2 tsp. salt', '2 tsp. basil', '2 tsp. oregano', '1 Tbsp. chili powder', '1 can kidney beans , drained', '1 carrot , chopped', '1 (8 oz.) rotini noodles , cooked', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(4274, ' Place potatoes and onion in a 4-quart saucepan. Cover with about 6 cups of water , butter , salt and pepper to taste. Cook until potatoes are done (about 15 to 20 minutes). Drain water until potatoes are just covered. Add milk and soups. Heat should be very low at this point. Cook only until thoroughly heated. Garnish with bacon and cheese.', '6 to 8 potatoes , peeled and diced', '1 small onion , chopped finely', '1 (16 oz.) can evaporated milk', '2 cans cream of chicken soup', '1 can cream of celery soup', ' butter , salt and pepper to taste', ' shredded cheese', ' crumbled bacon or bacon bits', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(4276, ' Cook the first 5 ingredients until tender. Then add celery soup , Veg-All and cheese. Simmer until cheese melts.', '1 qt. water', '2 c. potatoes , cubed', '1 c. onion , chopped', '1/2 c. celery , chopped', '4 bouillon cubes (chicken)', '2 cans celery soup', '1 can Veg-All , drained', '1 lb. Velveeta cheese', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
