(13205, ' Grease and flour 9 x 13 x 2 pan. Sprinkle pecans and coconut over bottom of pan. Mix cake mix according to package directions. Pour batter over coconut and pecans. Mix together butter , cream cheese and confectioners sugar. Drop this mixture by teaspoon on top of cake batter. DO NOT STIR, As cake bakes , it will envelope this mixture , creating a filling. Bake in 350&deg; preheated oven for approximately 45 minutes. Allow cake to cool in pan before cutting and serving.', '1 c. chopped pecans', '1 c. coconut', ' German chocolate cake mix', '1 stick butter , softened', '1 (8 oz.) pkg. softened cream cheese', '1 lb. box confectioners sugar (2 c.)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
