(13313, ' Dissolve jello in 3/4 c. boiling water , add 1/2 cup cold water; set aside at room temperature. Mix and bake cake as directed in 9 x 13 inch pan. Cool cake 20 - 25 minutes. Poke deep holes through top of warm wake while still in pan about 1 inch apart. Slowly pour gelatin mixture into holes. Refrigerate.', '1 (3 oz.) box lime jello', '1 pkg. lemon cake mix', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
