(13397, ' Mix eggs , oil (or applesauce) , sour cream and cake mix well and pour 1/2 batter in 9 x 13 pan. Take cinnamon and mix with brown sugar. Sprinkle on batter. Then pour rest of batter in pan. Cook at 350&deg; for 35 to 40 minutes. Cool 30 minutes. Mix 1 cup powdered sugar and 1/4 cup milk. Punch holes in cake and pour on. You''re ready. Enjoy the cake.', '4 eggs', '2/3 c. oil or applesauce', '1 c. sour cream', '1 Tbsp. cinnamon', '1 c. brown sugar', ' yellow cake mix', '1 c. powdered sugar', '1/4 c. milk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
