(19321, ' Saut&eacute; chicken strips in vegetable oil until done. Roll pizza dough out in a rectangle. Spread out chicken strips lengthwise on dough. Sprinkle with green onions , salt , pepper and Monterey Jack cheese. Roll up from long side of dough. Slice with serrated knife into 8 pieces. Bake in 400&deg; oven for 8 to 10 minutes. Serve hot.', '2 Tbsp. vegetable oil', '3 boneless chicken breasts , cut in strips', '1 pkg. frozen pizza dough', '1/2 c. chopped green onion', '1/4 tsp. salt', '1/8 tsp. black pepper', '1 c. Monterey Jack cheese , grated', '1 can chopped green chilies', '1 1/2 c. green onion , chopped', '2 tsp. vegetable oil', '1/2 c. sour cream', '1/4 tsp. salt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
