(19380, ' Mix the cream cheese , sour cream , oregano and crushed red pepper. Spread in bottom of pan. Cover with pizza sauce. Sprinkle onion , green pepper and pepperoni on top. Bake at 350&deg; for 15 minutes. Top with Mozzarella and return to oven. Remove when cheese has melted. Serve hot with crackers , bread sticks or garlic bread.', '8 oz. cream cheese', '1/2 c. sour cream', '1/2 tsp. oregano', '1/2 c. pizza sauce', '1/8 tsp. crushed red pepper', '1/2 c. chopped onion', '1/2 c. chopped green pepper', '1/2 c. chopped pepperoni', '1/2 c. Mozzarella cheese', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
