(19421, ' Mix taco seasoning with refried beans. Spread in bottom of square glass pan. Add in order: onion dip , sour cream , ripe olives , tomatoes , green chiles and Monterey Jack cheese. Use large Fritos to dip.', '1 pkg. taco seasoning', '1 can refried beans', '1 (8 oz.) onion dip', '1 (8 oz.) sour cream', '1 can chopped ripe olives', '2 large tomatoes , diced', '1 can chopped green chiles', '1 pkg. grated Monterey Jack cheese', ' Fritos', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
