(19442, ' Brown chuck in skillet , drain. Add 1/2 c salsa and taco seasoning mix. In casserole dish , layer tortilla chips , 1/2 ground chuck , chopped tomatoes and shredded cheese. Repeat layers. Bake at 400&deg; until cheese melts. Top with sour cream , salsa , and guacamole.', '1 lb ground chuck', '1/2 c salsa', '1 pkg taco seasoning mix', '1 bag favorite tortilla chips', ' kraft mexican style taco shredded cheese', ' chopped tomatoes', ' toppings: sour cream , salsa , guacamole', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(19444, ' Lay tostitos in a single layer on cookie sheet. Spread each with layer of enchilada dip , picante dip , and cheese. Place under broiler until cheese melts. Watch carefully to avoid burning chips. Have a cold drink nearby when getting ready to eat. Good for a quick and easy snack.', '1 bag round tostitos', '1 small can enchilada dip', '1 can picante dip', '1 c or more shredded sharp cheese', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
