(19671, ' Soften cheese with fork and room temperature. Add onion soup mix; rinse shrimp and mix in. Slowly add sour cream to right consistency. If made the night before , cheese will stiffen so add more sour cream before serving. Best to let set overnight for stronger serving.', '1/2 pt. sour cream', '1 pkg. Lipton onion soup mix', '1 (8 oz.) pkg. cream cheese (for more dip , add more cheese)', '2 cans cocktail shrimp , fresh or frozen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
