(19754, ' Mix cream cheese and seasoning mix. Spread on bottom of 9-inch pie plate or quiche dish. Layer guacamole , salsa , lettuce , cheese , onions and olives over cream cheese mixture. Serve immediately. Refrigerate any remaining dip. Serve with tortilla chips. Serves 6.', '1 (8 oz.) pkg. cream cheese , softened', '1 Tbsp. taco seasoning mix (your favorite brand)', '1 c. prepared guacamole (make your own or use ready-made)', '1 c. tomato-based salsa', '1 c. shredded lettuce', '1 c. shredded Cheddar cheese', '1/2 c. chopped green onions', '1 (2 oz.) can sliced black olives', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
