(23407, ' Slightly thaw bread or rolls , enough to spread out on baking dish. Spread amount of sauce you desire on the dough. Add any toppings you like. Bake at 350&deg; for 20 to 25 minutes , depending on thickness of your crust.', ' Rhodes frozen bread loaves or Texas rolls', ' Mozzarella cheese , shredded', ' Cheddar cheese , shredded', ' Monterey Jack cheese , shredded', ' Contadina pizza sauce (comes in squeeze bottle)', ' ground beef , browned', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
