(62789, ' Pour cereals into large bowl; set aside. In 1-quart microwave-safe bowl , combine chocolate chips , peanut butter and margarine. Microwave on High for 1 to 1 1/2 minutes or until smooth , stirring after 1 minute. Stir in vanilla. Pour chocolate mixture over cereals , stirring , until all pieces are evenly coated. Pour cereal mixture into a large resealable bag with powdered sugar. Seal securely and shake until all pieces are well coated. Spread on waxed paper to cool.', '9 c. your favorite Chex cereal', '1 c. semi-sweet chocolate chips', '1/2 c. peanut butter', '1 tsp. vanilla extract', '1 1/2 c. powdered sugar', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(62986, ' Beat eggs until frothy (about 1 minute). Add milk and mustard , set aside. Combine flour , baking powder and salt. Add to egg mixture and stir until thoroughly mixed. Fold in crabmeat. Add cheese cubes. Bake in uncovered 9 X 5 X 3 loaf pan at 350 degrees for 55-60 minutes. Test with toothpick for doneness. Cool for 10-15 minutes. Slice and top with salsa. Slices reheats and freezes well.', '6 eggs', '3/4 cup milk', '1 tsp. prepared mustard', '2-1/2 tsp. baking powder', '1-1/2 cup flour', '1/4 tsp. salt', '4 oz. Sharp Cheddar Cheese 1/4 inch cubes', '4 oz. Monterey Jack Pepper Cheese 1/4 inch cubes', '1/2 lb. Crabmeat (preferably lump)', ' Favorite salsa', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(63048, ' Pour water in electric blender container. Add gelatin dessert mix. Cover and blend at medium speed for one minute. Scrape sides of container. With machine running , add ice cream by spoonfuls through hole in lid of blender. Add milk and ice; blend at medium speed for 30 seconds. Serve immediately. Makes 3 to 4 servings.', '1/2 c. boiling water', '1 (4 oz.) pkg. gelatin dessert mix (any flavor)', '2 c. vanilla ice cream', '1 c. milk', '1/2 c. crushed ice', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
