(70331, ' Brown meat with onions and peppers and drain. Add sauce and simmer. Cook noodles and drain. Layer meat , noodles , mushrooms , cheese and pepperoni in crock pot. Cook on low for 90 minutes.', '1 1/2 pounds hamburger', '2 small jars pizza sauce', '1 bag pizza cheese', '1 can mushrooms', '1 chopped onion', '1 chopped green pepper', '1 large bag noodles', '1 package pepperoni', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
