(78656, ' Prepare orange juice , lemonade , and kool-aid according to package directions. In large pot , combine all 3 with pineapple juice. Heat 2 c water and 3 1/2 c sugar until boiling and sugar has melted. Add to juice mixture. Allow to cool and then freeze. Makes 2 gallons. Before serving in punch bowl , pour about 2 c ginger ale over slush.', '1 large frozen orange juice concentrate', '1 large frozen lemonade concentrate', '1 46 oz can pineapple juice', '1 Pre-sweetened pkg strawberry kool-aid', '2 c water', '3 1/2 c sugar', ' ginger ale', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
