(78923, ' Preheat oven to 400&deg;. Place English muffins , crust side down , on a cookie sheet. Spread each muffin half with 2 tablespoons pizza sauce. Top sauce with green pepper , mushrooms and onion. Sprinkle each muffin half with 2 tablespoons shredded cheese. Put on cookie sheet in oven. Bake 5 minutes. Bake until cheese is bubbling. Baking time might vary. Makes 4 small pizzas.', '2 English muffins , split in half', '1/2 c. prepared pizza sauce', '1 Tbsp. chopped green pepper', '1 Tbsp. sliced mushrooms', '1 Tbsp. chopped onions', '1/2 c. shredded Mozzarella cheese', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
