(114054, ' Heat oven or grill to 350&deg;. Place piece of fish on foil (make into &quot;boat&quot;). Sprinkle with dill , salt and pepper and olive oil. Place selection of fresh or frozen veggies on top of fish. Close up foil and place on cookie sheet (if using oven) and cook 20-30 minutes depending on thickness of fish. Serve with rice.', ' fresh fish (Grouper , Hogfish , Wahoo)', ' fresh or frozen veggies (carrots , broccoli , cauliflower , peppers , tomatoes , etc)', ' dill (about 1 Tbsp.)', ' olive oil (about 1/4 cup)', ' salt and pepper to taste', ' foil - 4 pieces', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(114055, ' One piece of foil per serving. Lay fresh fish on foil and shape into &quot;boat&quot;. Add 2-3 Tbsp. chutney on top of fish. Sprinkle with curry powder to taste. Layer with fresh veggies. Sprinkle with salt and pepper and about 2 Tbsp. chicken broth. Dot with butter , if desired. Bake at 400&deg; for 20 minutes or place on hot grill for 20-25 minutes. Serve with rice.', ' fresh fish', ' sliced tomatoes , peppers , onions', ' mango chutney', ' curry', ' salt and pepper', ' chicken broth or chicken bouillon cube dissolved in water', ' butter (if desired)', ' foil', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(114059, ' Heat olive oil in skillet. Add garlic , salt , pepper , crushed red pepper. Let garlic lightly brown (do not burn garlic as it will have a bitter taste). Add tenderized conch and saut&eacute; for 1-3 minutes. Add wine and let reduce slightly. Add clam juice or stock and cook for 1 to 3 minutes longer. Add parsley and cooked linguine. Toss and serve immediately.', '1 cup tenderized and chopped conch', '1/3 cup olive oil', '2 Tbsp. garlic , chopped', ' salt and pepper (to taste)', ' crushed red pepper (to taste)', '1/4 to 1/2 cup fish stock or clam juice', '1/4 cup white wine', '2 Tbsp. fresh chopped parsley', '1/3 lb. linguine', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
