(114994, ' Prepare pasta as directed on package , adding broccoli to water during last 3 minutes of pasta cooking time; drain. Heat sauce and chicken breast strips in saucepan on medium heat 5 minutes or until thoroughly heated. Toss all ingredients. Makes 3 servings.', '1 (9 oz.) pkg. DiGiorno tortellini (any flavor)', '2 c. broccoli flowerets', '1 (10 oz.) pkg. DiGiorno Alfredo sauce', '1 (6 oz.) pkg. Louis Rich grilled chicken breast strips', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
