(146403, ' Scrub potatoes very good and slice into 8 wedges. Cover with boiling water and cook until tender. Remove from water and place onto a shallow baking sheet. Spray potatoes with Pam. Sprinkle seasoning over potatoes , use the amount that is suitable for your families'' taste. Turn oven on broil , place potatoes in oven until slightly brown. Serve hot. Makes about 4 servings.', '2 large baking potatoes', ' McCormick Grill Mates Seasoning', ' Butter flavor Pam cooking spray', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(146427, ' Saut&eacute;: celery or cream of celery soup , onions and green peppers. In a casserole dish put peas , mushroom soup , pimiento and water chestnuts. Mix well. Pour both mixtures in a casserole dish along with reserved juice from peas. Top with bread crumbs or crackers. Dot with butter. Bake at 350 degrees for 25 minutes.', '2- cans green party peas , drained , reserve juice', '1 stick margarine', '1 c. chopped celery or 1-can cream of celery soup , undiluted', '1 c. chopped onion', '1 c. chopped green pepper (optional)', '1 can mushroom soup', '1 small jar pimiento , chopped', '1 can water chestnuts , sliced', ' Bread crumbs or cracker crumbs', ' butter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(147232, ' Combine eggs , sugar , pumpkin , and lemon juice together. Then sift salt , flour , baking powder , cinnamon , and nutmeg over the mixture. After stirring everything together pour into a greased jelly roll or cookie sheet pan. Top with chopped pecans. Bake 15 minutes at 375&deg;. After baking , turn onto towel and roll , starting with the shorter end. Let cool in towel.', '3 eggs; beaten', '1 c. sugar', '2/3 c. pumpkin', '1 tsp. lemon juice', '1/2 tsp. salt', '3/4 c. flour', '2 tsp. baking powder', '2 tsp. cinnamon', '1/2 tsp. nutmeg', '1/2 c. pecans', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
