(191025, ' Brown hamburger and sausage together and drain well. Add garlic salt and Worcestershire sauce. Melt in Velveeta cheese. Spoon mixture onto slices of party rye bread. Broil for a few minutes. Serve immediately.', '1 lb. ground beef', '1 lb. hot sausage', '1 lb. Velveeta cheese', '1 loaf party rye bread', ' dash of garlic salt', '2 Tbsp. Worcestershire sauce', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
