(249546, ' To 1 tablespoon butter and a little water , add onion and cook slightly. Add ground pork. Cook with onion , but don''t brown. Add tomato soup , tomato juice , sugar , paprika , salt and pepper. Cook 10 minutes. Boil noodles and drain. Mix meat mixture and noodles together. Mix grated cheese through ingredients. Sprinkle some on top. Bake at 325&deg; for 1 hour. Makes 10 servings.', '2 onions , chopped', '1 1/2 lb. ground pork', '1 can tomato soup', '1 medium can tomato juice', '3 Tbsp. white sugar', ' dessert spoon paprika', ' salt and pepper (lots)', '8 oz. Cheddar cheese , grated', '1 pkg. noodles', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
