(300071, ' Dissolve gelatin and Tang in boiling water. Chill until slightly thickened. Fold in rest of ingredients and pour into a lightly greased 5-cup mold. Chill until firm.', '1 (3 oz.) pkg. sugar-free orange gelatin', '2 Tbsp. Tang', '1 3/4 c. boiling water', '1 (8 oz.) container dessert topping , thawed', '1 (8 oz.) can crushed pineapple , drained', '1 c. grated mild or sharp Cheddar cheese', '1/2 c. chopped pecans', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
