(347174, ' In mixer bowl , blend together cottage cheese and thawed topping. Beat until blended. Stir in dry gelatin. Fold in pineapple and mandarin oranges. Press into 7 or 8-cup mold. Chill several hours or overnight. Unmold onto serving plate; garnish with endive. Serves 12.', '3 c. cream-style cottage cheese', '1 qt. frozen whipped dessert topping , thawed', '2 (3 oz.) pkg. orange-pineapple flavored gelatin', '1 (13 1/2 oz.) can pineapple tidbits , drained', '1 (11 oz.) can mandarin orange sections , drained', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
