(434536, ' Mix beans and pepper juice (add some chopped pepper if desired) together in a bowl. Mix 2/3 of taco seasoning in it , too. Spread mixture in a dish or tray bottom (round plate like pizza looks great). Mix 1/3 of taco seasoning with sour cream and spread over bean mixture. Sprinkle the cheese and onion and tomato on top as desired. Olives or mushrooms can be added if desired.', '1 can refried beans', '1 jar jalapeno peppers (small jar)', '1 pkg. taco seasoning', '1 (16 oz.) carton sour cream', '1 medium tomato , chopped', '1 medium onion , chopped', '1 small can sliced olives and/or mushrooms', ' grated cheese', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
