(452618, ' Mix pudding and crushed pineapple (with juice) together. Let sit until dissolved. Gently stir in Cool Whip. Refrigerate until eaten. You can add chopped cherries for festive color.', '1 large pistachio pudding (instant)', '7 oz. crushed pineapple with juice (do not drain)', ' biggest bowl Cool Whip you can get or 2 small bowls', ' drained , halved maraschino cherries (if desired for Christmas)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
