(453461, ' Put bananas in blender. Bring sugar and water to boil and boil for 5 minutes. Cool. Add to juices and bananas. Put into 6 (1 quart) containers. Freeze.', '4 c. sugar', '6 c. water', '5 bananas', '2 small cans frozen lemonade', '2 small cans orange juice', '1 (46 oz.) can pineapple juice', '6 qt. ginger ale', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(453794, ' Mix graham cracker crumbs , 2 tablespoons sugar and enough melted margarine to hold the crumb mixture together. Press mixture into bottom and sides of spring-form pan. Place pan in freezer. Mix cream cheese , sugar , and cornstarch in mixer. Add egg and egg whites , then sour cream. Pour into spring-form pan. Place pan in preheated oven of 375&deg;. Bake for 10 minutes; turn oven to 300&deg;. Bake for 10 minutes. Turn oven to 225&deg;. Bake for 85 minutes. Turn oven off. Leave in oven for 45 minutes. Take out of oven. Cool completely , then refrigerate.', '3 (8 oz.) pkg. lite or no-fat cream cheese', '1 c. nonfat sour cream', '1 1/3 c. sugar', '1 1/2 Tbsp. cornstarch', '1 whole egg', '3 egg whites', '1 1/2 c. graham cracker crumbs', '2 Tbsp. sugar', ' margarine', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(454217, ' In blender or food processor , process beans to a paste consistency. In a shallow serving dish with a rim , layer the ingredients as follows: beans , sour cream , avocado dip , cheese , peppers , olives , scallions and tomatoes. Serve with taco chips.', '1 can chili beans', '1 small can jalapeno peppers , finely chopped (green chile peppers)', '1 c. sour cream', '1 container avocado dip', '1 c. Cheddar cheese , shredded', '1 bunch scallions , chopped', '1 (6 oz.) can pitted black olives , chopped', '2 medium tomatoes , diced', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(454482, ' Place Jell-O , water , cheese and marshmallows in large boiler and cook until dissolved. Remove from heat and add pineapple , nuts , milk , mayonnaise and banana. Pour into dish and place in refrigerator until congealed.', '1 pkg. lime Jell-O gelatin dessert or cherry Jell-O gelatin dessert', '3/4 c. boiling water', '1 small pkg. cream cheese', '14 large marshmallows', '1 small can crushed pineapple', '1/2 c. chopped nuts', '1/2 c. canned milk', '1/3 c. mayonnaise', '3/4 c. diced banana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
