(456047, ' Mix all of these ingredients together and depending on which kind of flour you use , you may want to add another 1/2 to 1 cup so the dough can be handled easily. Roll out and cut with doughnut cutter and fry in deep fat at 375&deg; until lightly brown on one side and turn carefully to brown on other side. Remove and drain on paper towel. May tip in sugar as these are not a very sweet item.', '1 can sweetened condensed milk', '2/3 c. sour milk with 1 1/2 tsp. baking soda', '3 1/2 c. flour', '2 eggs', '1/2 tsp. salt', '1 tsp. vanilla', '3 dessert spoons vegetable oil', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(456262, ' In a bowl , blend together 1 cup of the flour , the butter and 1/4 cup of the confectioners sugar until the mixture resembles meal. Pat the mixture into an 8-inch square baking pan and bake it in the middle of a preheated 350&deg; oven for 12 to 15 minutes or until it is a pale golden.', '1 c. plus 2 Tbsp. all-purpose flour', '1 stick (1/2 c.) cold , unsalted butter , cut into bits', '1/4 c. confectioners sugar , plus additional for sifting over the dessert', '2 large eggs', '3/4 c. granulated sugar', '3 Tbsp. fresh lemon juice', '1/2 tsp. double-acting baking powder', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(456503, ' Combine crumbs and melted butter; press into bottom of a 13 x 9 x 2-inch pan. Beat powdered sugar , cream cheese and the 1 cup butter 8 to 10 minutes (makes it fluffy). Add eggs; beat until fluffy. Spread over crust and arrange bananas over top; sprinkle with coconut. Spread dessert topping over all; sprinkle with nuts. Cover; chill several hours. Cut into squares. Garnish each serving with a candy cane and banana slices. Makes 12 servings.', '2 c. vanilla wafer crumbs', '1/2 c. melted butter or margarine', '2 c. sifted powdered sugar', '1 (8 oz.) pkg. cream cheese , softened', '1 c. butter or margarine , softened', '2 eggs', '4 medium bananas , sliced', '1 c. coconut', '1 (8 oz.) carton whipped dessert topping , thawed', '1 c. chopped walnuts', ' small candy canes (optional)', ' banana slices (optional)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
