(459959, ' Cover chicken wings with flour. Cook in iron skillet until done. let cool for 5 minutes , then soak the chicken wings with hot sauce.', '2 pkg. chicken wings , cut apart', '1 1/2 c. flour', '1/2 to 1 bottle Louisiana''s pure crystal hot sauce', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
