(475708, ' Mix 4 minutes. Bake in Bundt pan at 375&deg; for 40 to 45 minutes (until cake begins to pull away from pan). Cool 15 minutes. Remove from pan and sprinkle with powdered sugar.', '1 box Duncan Hines butter cake mix', '4 eggs', '3/4 c. oil', '1 jar junior baby food dessert', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(476206, ' Mix oil , sugar , vinegar and soy sauce and refrigerate. Mix all other ingredients you plan to use. Walnuts can be browned in butter on the stove in saucepan , but to avoid fat and calories , best use them as they are. Whatever ingredient combinations you use , this is a great salad.', ' romaine lettuce', ' chopped walnuts', '1 c. sugar', '3 Tbsp. soy sauce', ' chow mein noodles', '1 c. oil', '1/2 c. vinegar', '1 can mandarin oranges (optional)', '1 avocado (optional)', ' grilled chicken breast (optional)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(476688, ' Rinse chicken wings in cold water. Preheat oven to 350&deg;. Fold chicken wings and place one layer thick in large Corning Ware. Cover with teriyaki sauce for &quot;T&quot; Wings. Add Amaretto to teriyaki sauce; mix and cover chicken with mixture for &quot;T &amp; A&quot; Wings. Cover and cook for 90 minutes until done. Turn wings every 20 minutes. Drain , cool and serve.', ' pkg. of 10 chicken wings', '1/3 c. teriyaki sauce', '2 oz. Amaretto', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(476821, ' Dissolve yeast in warm water. Add sugar , oil and salt; mix well , adding flour last. Let rise in a warm place , covered. Form into desired shapes in greased cup cake pans or in pie plates. Let rise again , about 1/2 hour. Bake at 350&deg; for 20 minutes. This dough may be used to make pizza shells.', '1 cake household yeast', '2 1/2 c. warm water', '1/2 c. sugar', '1/2 c. oil', '1 tsp. salt', '8 c. flour', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
