(482204, ' Mix flour and salt. Blend oil in thoroughly with a fork. Sprinkle water over mixture; mix well. Press dough firmly into a ball with hands. If too dry , mix in 1 or 2 tablespoons more oil.', '2 c. sifted flour', '1/2 c. corn oil', '1 tsp. salt', '3 Tbsp. cold water', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
