(490270, ' Stir 2 cups boiling water into red gelatin in medium bowl for 2 minutes or until completely dissolved. Stir in half the cold water. Pour into 6-cup mold. Refrigerate for 1 1/4 hours or until slightly thickened. Spoon over marshmallows. Refrigerate for 3 hours or until firm. Unmold. Garnish with whipped topping.', '4 c. boiling water', '1 pkg. Jell-O brand gelatin (any red flavor)', '1 c. cold water', '1 1/2 c. Kraft miniature marshmallows', '1 pkg. Jell-O brand berry blue flavor gelatin dessert', ' Cool Whip', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
