(849899, ' In 9 x 13-inch pan , break up angel food cake in small pieces. Mix pudding with 2 cups skim milk. Add frozen yogurt to pudding. Pour over cake and set in refrigerator approximately 1/2 hour. Mix 2 packages jello with 2 cups boiling water. Add strawberries. Pour over top of cake. Refrigerate overnight or until set. Serves 16.', ' angel food cake (prepare or buy pre-made)', '2 pkg. instant vanilla pudding', '2 c. skim milk', '1 qt. nonfat frozen vanilla yogurt', '2 small pkg. strawberry jello', '2 (10 oz.) pkg. frozen strawberries (no sugar added)', '2 c. boiling water', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(851388, ' Dinner Rolls: Mix first 3 ingredients in large bowl with boiling water until dissolved. Add eggs , then water and yeast mixture , then flour. If you need more flour to make dough medium consistency. Refrigerate overnight. Dinner rolls are made by greasing 2 dozen muffin tins. Then roll into small balls with 2 or 3. Let rise with towel covering rolls for 2 1/2 or 3 hours. Bake at 350&deg; for 10 to 15 minutes , until tops and bottom are brown.', '3/4 c. sugar', '1 tsp. salt', '3/4 c. Crisco', '1 c. boiling water', '2 well beaten eggs', '2 pkg. yeast , dissolved in 1 c. water (105~ to 115~)', '6 c. unsifted flour', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(852147, ' Blend thoroughly the first 5 ingredients. Fold together sacrificial giving and kindly service. Gently mix altogether and season with tears of joy , sorrow and compassion. Laughter will rise when mixture is correct. Time redeemed wisely will satisfy the hunger of starved souls. Omit all fault finding of self and others.', ' immeasurable amounts faith in God', ' immeasurable amounts prayer', ' immeasurable amounts praise', ' immeasurable amounts thanksgiving', ' immeasurable amounts forgiveness (self and others)', ' immeasurable amounts sacrificial giving', ' immeasurable amounts kindly service', ' immeasurable amounts tears and laughter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(853554, ' Cook onion and celery in olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat , stirring constantly , until tender. Add chicken broth and dried thyme; bring mixture to a boil. Rinse wild rice in 3 changes of hot water; drain. Add wild rice to broth mixture. Cover. Reduce heat and cook 30 minutes. Add black-eyed peas and next 7 ingredients; cover and cook 20 minutes or until rice is tender. Serve with grilled pork medallions and apple wedges. Garnish , if desired. Yields 4 servings.', '3/4 c. chopped onion', '1/2 c. chopped celery', '1 tsp. olive oil', '2 (16 oz.) cans ready-to-serve reduced-sodium fat free chicken broth', '1 tsp. dried thyme', '1/2 c. wild rice (uncooked)', '1 c. frozen black-eyed peas', '1/2 c. long grain rice (uncooked)', '3/4 c. chopped tomato', '2 tsp. lemon juice', '2 Tbsp. chopped fresh parsley', '1/2 tsp. salt', '1/4 tsp. ground red pepper', '1/4 tsp. freshly ground black pepper', ' grilled pork medallions', '1 Red Delicious apple , cut into 12 wedges', ' garnish (fresh thyme sprigs)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
