(937246, ' Cut eggs in half lengthwise; scoop out yolks into small mixing bowl and mash with a fork. Add remaining ingredients and mix well. Spoon yolk mixture into egg white halves. Chill until ready to serve.', '1 doz. eggs , hard-boiled', '1/2 c. frozen , chopped spinach , thawed and drained', '1/4 c. mayonnaise', '1/4 c. imitation bacon bits', '2 1/2 Tbsp. apple cider vinegar', '2 Tbsp. margarine , softened', '1 Tbsp. sugar', '2 tsp. black pepper', '1/4 tsp. salt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
